Author: lhadnil
Text: I “accidentally maintained” by binging and restricting the same five lbs all of last year :))))))))))) feeling great  my BMI is 27 I think lol

Author: dostoyefski
Text: At 5’7” there’s no way your maintenance is 1,000, are you definitely tracking your calories accurately? Even if you are I’m sure there’s an explanation for this. I recently found out that my weekly binge brought my average daily calories over the space of a week up from 800 to 1,400ish (cue screaming)
